mg_puddle_jumpers_v3_rev11 << SPAWNS FOR 60+ players! <<
Minigame map with usable objects from TV series - "Stargate". Features: - Space Bases ( 3x ) - Puddle Jumpers ( 2x - usable ) - Stargates ( 2x - fully usable ) - Ring transporters ( 4x - usable ) - A lot of fun :D Thanks for playing, i hope you like this map. Im agree to decompile map, and use their objects on other maps, but please write in credits or on the map my nickname - i will give all sources of map ( VMF + textures + models + sounds = open source ) :)
